[[#blogit_entrybody]]One of the additions to Scribus 1.4 will be a lot of new Color Palettes... but one will be missing.

While Christmas was getting closer and closer, I was wondering if we shouldn't at least have a Panettone Color Palette:

Attach:{Blog.Panettone-for-Scribus$FullName}/panettone.png

Somebody was faster than me: Olivier Berten has announced his new script @@Pantone.py@@, which runs inside of Scribus, has a nice interface and downloads the Colors directly from the Pantone website. [[http://www.selapa.net/scribus/|Check it out!]]

Attach:{$FullName}/pantone_py.png

Let's see who will be first to sue us: [[http://www.bauli.it/en|Bauli]] or [[http://www.pantone.com|Pantone]]?

Buona Befana![[#blogit_entrybodyend]]
